        </div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 leading-tight bg-gradient-to-r from-green-600 to-blue-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          How to Choose the Right AI Chatbot for Your Needs
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Step-by-step guide to selecting the perfect AI chatbot. Compare features, pricing, 
          and use cases to make an informed decision that saves you time and money.
        </p>
        
        <!-- Key Benefits Box -->
        <div class="bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-400 p-6 rounded-r-lg mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-900 mb-3">🎯 What You'll Learn</h3>
          <ul class="text-green-800 space-y-2 text-sm">
            <li>• Complete decision framework with scoring system</li>
            <li>• Real-world testing methodology and results</li>
            <li>• Cost analysis including hidden expenses</li>
            <li>• Common mistakes that cost businesses thousands</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </header>

